dct_title_s: MCTS Bus Routes Milwaukee County, Wisconsin 2008
dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents the MCTS bus routes for Milwaukee, Wisconsin in 2008. The dataset was originally published by the Milwaukee County Transit System (MCTS) in 2008.
